Sunt complet falit

191
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:29,083
Dă-te jos!

192
00:19:29,166 --> 00:19:30,458
Treci la cărbuni!

193
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:37,291
Haide, Trudy!

194
00:19:39,208 --> 00:19:41,916
- Repede, Trudy!
- Țineți ritmul, doamnelor!

195
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:44,250
